high_descs: Turn and face the sink to the left.
Pick the tomato up from the counter in front of the sink.
Turn to the left and face the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave and shut the door and then take the tomato out and shut the door.
Turn around and cross the room and turn to the left to face the fridge.
Put the tomato in the fridge and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk up to the oven, then turn right and walk over to the sink.
Pick up the tomato off of the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave and turn it on, after a couple seconds remove the now heated tomato and close the microwave.
Turn around and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the heated tomato inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: turn around, head to the sink
take the tomato from the counter
turn to the left, open the microwave
put the tomato in the microwave, close the door
turn on the microwave for 3 seconds, open the door, take out the tomato, close the door
turn around, head to the fridge, put the tomato inside the fridge
anns.task_desc: cook the tomato for 3 seconds, put it in the fridge
